*Momenat je bio veoma kratak. (The moment was very short.)
Odmah u momenat smo shvatili da nismo u pravu. (We immediately realized that we were wrong in that moment.)
On je za trenutak zastao. (He stopped for a moment.)
Biće tu još mnogo trenutaka kada će nam biti potrebna tvoja pomoć. (There will be many more moments when we will need your help.)
U momenat je shvatio svoju grešku. (He realized his mistake in a moment.)